    {"type":"text","id":"lgt","x":1058,"y":312,"width":300,"height":24,"text":"图例 · ≈传统 · emerge 实例","fontSize":17,"fontFamily":1,"strokeColor":"#343a40","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top"},
    {"type":"text","id":"lgb","x":1058,"y":348,"width":310,"height":320,"text":"意图　≈ GUI　·　chat / 命令\n\nAgent 内核　= CPU　·　Claude\n\n程序　≈ 源代码　·　SKILL.md\n（改一句话就改了软件）\n\n能力　≈ SDK 调用　·　extract·score·ws_*\n\n上下文+记忆　= RAM　·　Active context·reviewed\n\n文件系统总线　= 磁盘　·　project.json·models·predictions\n\n纠正闭环　·　score·save_reviewed·autoresearch\n\n能力包　·　/plugin install · Upload plugin","fontSize":15,"fontFamily":1,"strokeColor":"#495057","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top"},

